  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>'LumineNight'</strong> is a <strong>mystery adventure game</strong> set in the city of Summerset, USA, in the 1950s. You can play as Detective Kelvin Foster and his only daughter, self-proclaimed Detective Selen Foster, to unravel the secrets of a series of unresolved murders over a decade. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players need to <strong>investigate</strong>, <strong>solve puzzles and codes</strong>, <strong>infiltrate</strong>, <strong>interrogate</strong>, and <strong>deduce the truth</strong>, all based on the following five <strong>detective principles:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>1. Find Clues in Dark Streets</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/a277b3a571307eae9f811fd294333042.poster.avif?t=1768804847\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/a277b3a571307eae9f811fd294333042.webm?t=1768804847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/a277b3a571307eae9f811fd294333042.mp4?t=1768804847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/f2a912199bf15aaf648d70be618ea1c0.poster.avif?t=1768804847\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/f2a912199bf15aaf648d70be618ea1c0.webm?t=1768804847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/f2a912199bf15aaf648d70be618ea1c0.mp4?t=1768804847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In a corrupted city's darkness, the detective's eyes are the only thing you can trust.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the deep night, the neon-lit streets are filled with truths yet to be uncovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gathering raw evidence is the mother of all detective work.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Detectives who pursue the truth <strong>prowl through the city</strong> in the night's darkness, <strong>gathering</strong> even the slightest clue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>2. Use All Your Senses to Unravel Tricks and Codes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/7ff927095ce8041c107ad51cf5f121c7.avif?t=1768804847\" width=600 height=338 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/b69bbfbb29b5cb6aba529adea5484e88.poster.avif?t=1768804847\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/b69bbfbb29b5cb6aba529adea5484e88.webm?t=1768804847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/b69bbfbb29b5cb6aba529adea5484e88.mp4?t=1768804847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nothing can stand in the way of those seeking the truth.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A piece of advice from a father to his daughter, a genius in deciphering codes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Riddles</strong> and <strong>puzzles</strong> encountered during the investigation, doors that are firmly locked and won't open, <strong>codes</strong> containing secrets that penetrate all truths...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everything awaits the touch of a solver.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>3. Sneak among the Shadows</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/3fbaf7c772c591079ccdd004f7225ef1.poster.avif?t=1768804847\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/3fbaf7c772c591079ccdd004f7225ef1.webm?t=1768804847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/3fbaf7c772c591079ccdd004f7225ef1.mp4?t=1768804847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>As a detective, sometimes you should act before getting permission.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you secretly <strong>infiltrate</strong> and bypass strict security, you might be able to access <strong>crucial clues</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>4. Prove Contradictions Between the Crime Scene and Testimonies</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/f49230b21761e4c1c58f043d4ef01ac2.poster.avif?t=1768804847\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/f49230b21761e4c1c58f043d4ef01ac2.webm?t=1768804847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/f49230b21761e4c1c58f043d4ef01ac2.mp4?t=1768804847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/77e37ff8e2441c01757fd862d75e190d.poster.avif?t=1768804847\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/77e37ff8e2441c01757fd862d75e190d.webm?t=1768804847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/77e37ff8e2441c01757fd862d75e190d.mp4?t=1768804847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If there are manipulated traces in the crime scene or testimonies that do not align, you can verify the contradicting aspects through interrogation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you refute the contradictions with your logic, the masks of those riddled with lies will be stripped away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>5. Complete the Deduction</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/0159adf451d1d549410063250140bfc7.poster.avif?t=1768804847\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/0159adf451d1d549410063250140bfc7.webm?t=1768804847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/0159adf451d1d549410063250140bfc7.mp4?t=1768804847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/e354a439183d70ed54eb7f1a70370142.poster.avif?t=1768804847\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/e354a439183d70ed54eb7f1a70370142.webm?t=1768804847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/e354a439183d70ed54eb7f1a70370142.mp4?t=1768804847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can <strong>deduce</strong> the beginning and end of all incidents, the reality behind secrets, and what each character wanted to hide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Revealing the truth now <strong>depends upon you</strong>.</p>",
